{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban mid-contract price hikes on mobile phones and home broadband",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "A contract is a contract so how can it be right that greedy companies can put prices up mid term? It needs looking at as we believe this surely shouldn't be legal.",
